    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use the Fitness Track Application.</p>

    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> This includes your name, email address, and other information you provide when registering or using the app.</li>
        <li><strong>Workout Data:</strong> Information related to your workouts, goals, and progress reports, which is linked to your user account.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Data about how you interact with the app, including your IP address, browser type, and operating system.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>Your information may be used for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and maintain our services, including tracking workouts and progress.</li>
        <li>To send you updates, newsletters, and promotional materials related to training and fitness programs.</li>
        <li>To improve our app and enhance user experience based on feedback and usage patterns.</li>
        <li>To monitor the usage of our application and detect any potential issues.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
    <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information in the following cases:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>With service providers who assist us in operating our application and conducting our business.</li>
        <li>When required by law, to comply with legal obligations or to protect our rights and safety.</li>
        <li>In connection with a merger, sale, or acquisition of all or a portion of our assets.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>4. Data Security</h3>
    <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

    <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access the personal information we hold about you.</li>
        <li>Request corrections to any inaccuracies in your personal data.</li>
        <li>Withdraw your consent to our processing of your data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. Your continued use of the app after any modifications constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>

